{"tid":1218260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新Online Game介紹: 真．香港保衛戰","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:57:17.000Z","uid":79109,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca74c70652bfbbe57dc168413bd53d86ad37e7b","tid":1218260,"uid":79109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:23:03.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到有隻新Online Game前幾日出左，叫<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">真．香港保衛戰</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻Game好似係俾玩家有唔同<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>職業</strong></span>，咁多款職業俾你選擇，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一定有岩你既</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似分三大類: <span style=\"color: teal;\">前</span> <span style=\"color: pink;\">後</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">自由</span><br />\n前既有:<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">盾佬</span> (HP高配<span style=\"color: gold;\">盾</span>) 打機無Tank邊得呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">片手戰士</span> (可以拎單手<span style=\"color: gold;\">傘</span>，攻守數值平衡)<br />\n<br />\n後既有:<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">投擲手</span> (人肉投擲水樽等<span style=\"color: gold;\">殺害力超低</span>既雜物，以攻擊速度同人數見識)<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">旗手</span>(拎住顥眼既香港區旗，常局於部曲既中央位置，大大提升各士兵既位置感)<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">大聲公</span> (配備電子/人肉大聲公，一眼關七，<span style=\"color: gold;\">提點各方士兵如何走位</span>)<br />\n<br />\n自由:<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">律師</span> (需要點爆學識，通常會好似218五個零咁留低自己既聯絡資料)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">大富豪</span>(同Bruce Wayne一樣，有錢就係佢既超能力，默默為士兵<span style=\"color: gold;\">提供各種裝備)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">牧師</span> (多以群體出陣，勁起上黎好似阿叔林尚義咁帶住成班信徒<span style=\"color: gold;\">以詩歌同聖經經文作出持續攻擊</span>)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">紀曉嵐</span> (單人型牧師，轉以個人<span style=\"color: gold;\">道德情操等嘗試教化</span>對方將領或士兵，持久力可謂金槍不倒)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">通訊兵</span> (<span style=\"color: gold;\">轉達重要資訊</span>)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">外交兵</span> 游說更多身邊認識既人，得到佢地既不反對、解諒或支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意事項:<br />\n1. 目標得一個，你知、我知、所有人都知<br />\n2. 有唔同場地，唔同層數同日子，但<strong>勝利或失敗只有一個</strong><br />\n3. 保護自己同眼前所有同伴 (無事先能達成目標)<br />\n4.  <strong>兵貴神速</strong>，佔得太大地方只會得到負作用既<br />\n5. NPC有學習能力，玩家必須有比NPC更高既學習能力同增強速力方能獲勝<br />\n6. 記得自己度下買咩Skin同防具，一早準備好點都好過係地下執裝<br />\n7. 選完職唔洗周圍同人講，自己埋位<br />\n8. <strong>呢隻太少玩家加入，就會Del Server，想加入就盡快</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n果D點<span style=\"color: gold;\">排陣</span>個D，我少玩即時戰略遊戲，交俾熟識既巴打睇下有無發到夢啦?"},{"pid":"18dc1d103e4f8bcc548c55c65b64f72068c3746b","tid":1218260,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"仲有鍵盤戰士，可以好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n注意力係有限資源，連登主頁show post數亦有限<br />\n希望LIHKG高流量時大家只覆有用post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【經驗總結】 尋日出過幾輪文宣，小弟有啲嘢想同連登嘅鍵盤戰士講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1212748/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1212748/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"3fd0d10e281a6c8ee8af8ee82c8e83db1206c774","tid":1218260,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"6bc72fbfef1607ab52f2679b0141c101fd889ead","tid":1218260,"uid":79109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"唔該推俾對呢種好遊戲無概念既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}